Constructor Detail

PropertyProjection

public PropertyProjection(java.lang.String propertyName,
                          java.lang.Class<?> type)
Constructs a property projection. If type is specified, RawValue.asType(Class) will be used to restore the original value of the property. Otherwise instances of RawValue will be returned.

Parameters:
propertyName - The name of the property to project
type - The type of values stored in the projected properties or if the type is not known or variable. If null, RawValues are returned.
